CRITICAL — ANTI-REASONING-PREAMBLE INSTRUCTIONS (R1-Distill-specific):

DeepSeek-R1-Distill models emit a "thinking" preamble by default
(e.g., "Okay, so I need to summarize..." or `<think>...</think>` blocks).
This breaks downstream consumers and eats the output token budget.

To prevent that, your entire response MUST be exactly one
`<summary>...</summary>` block, with nothing before or after it.

- DO NOT think out loud, explain your reasoning, restate the task,
